---
import Technique from '../../../components/Technique.astro';
import ProsCons from '../../../components/ProsCons.astro';
import Callout from '../../../components/Callout.astro';
import Chip from '../../../components/Chip.astro';
import Accordion from '../../../components/Accordion.astro';
import KeyTakeaway from '../../../components/KeyTakeaway.astro';
import QuoteBlock from '../../../components/QuoteBlock.astro';
import StepList from '../../../components/StepList.astro';
import Timeline from '../../../components/Timeline.astro';
import WhyImportant from '../../../components/WhyImportant.astro';
---

  <section class="component-group" id="group-content">
    <header class="component-group__header">
      <h2>Nội dung &amp; nhấn mạnh</h2>
      <p>
        Khối kỹ thuật, rationale, callout/chip, takeaway và trích dẫn, accordion, checklist bước và timeline.
      </p>
    </header>

  {/* ─────── Technique ─────── */}
  <section class="showcase-section" id="technique">
    <h3>Technique</h3>
    <div class="example-render">
      <Technique
        id="demo-t1"
        title="Kỹ thuật demo"
        tid="A.1"
        location='File: <code>src/agent/loop.ts:1-42</code>'
      >
        <p>Nội dung technique. Thường chứa WhyImportant + code + ProsCons + RefList.</p>
      </Technique>
    </div>
    <pre class="example-code"><code>{`<Technique
  id="t1"
  title="1. Kỹ thuật X"
  tid="A.1"
  location='File: <code>src/agent/loop.ts:120-180</code>'
>
  <WhyImportant>...</WhyImportant>
  <CodeBlock>...</CodeBlock>
  <ProsCons pros={[...]} cons={[...]} />
  <RefList items={[...]} />
</Technique>`}</code></pre>
  </section>

  {/* ─────── WhyImportant ─────── */}
  <section class="showcase-section" id="whyimportant">
    <h3>WhyImportant</h3>
    <div class="example-render">
      <WhyImportant>
        <strong>Tại sao quan trọng.</strong> Giải thích rationale 2-3 câu.
      </WhyImportant>
    </div>
    <pre class="example-code"><code>{`<WhyImportant>
  <strong>Tại sao quan trọng.</strong> Giải thích 2-3 câu.
</WhyImportant>`}</code></pre>
  </section>

  {/* ─────── ProsCons ─────── */}
  <section class="showcase-section" id="proscons">
    <h3>ProsCons</h3>
    <div class="example-render">
      <ProsCons
        pros={[
          'Ưu điểm 1',
          'Ưu điểm 2 có <code>inline code</code>',
        ]}
        cons={[
          'Nhược 1',
          'Nhược 2 với <a href="#">link</a>',
        ]}
      />
    </div>
    <pre class="example-code"><code>{`<ProsCons
  pros={['Ưu 1', 'Ưu 2 có <code>inline</code>']}
  cons={['Nhược 1', 'Nhược 2 với <a href="#">link</a>']}
/>`}</code></pre>
  </section>

  {/* ─────── Callout ─────── */}
  <section class="showcase-section" id="callout">
    <h3>Callout</h3>
    <div class="example-render">
      <Callout type="info"><strong>Info</strong> — ghi chú thường.</Callout>
      <Callout type="warn"><strong>Warn</strong> — lưu ý / pitfall.</Callout>
      <Callout type="unique"><strong>Unique</strong> — điểm khác biệt.</Callout>
      <Callout type="success"><strong>Success</strong> — kết luận tích cực.</Callout>
    </div>
    <pre class="example-code"><code>{`<Callout type="info">...</Callout>
<Callout type="warn">...</Callout>
<Callout type="unique">...</Callout>
<Callout type="success">...</Callout>`}</code></pre>
  </section>

  {/* ─────── Chip ─────── */}
  <section class="showcase-section" id="chip">
    <h3>Chip</h3>
    <div class="example-render">
      <Chip>default</Chip>{' '}
      <Chip variant="green">green</Chip>{' '}
      <Chip variant="amber">amber</Chip>{' '}
      <Chip variant="purple">purple</Chip>{' '}
      <Chip variant="cyan">cyan</Chip>{' '}
      <Chip variant="red">red</Chip>{' '}
      <Chip variant="unique">unique</Chip>
    </div>
    <pre class="example-code"><code>{`<Chip>default</Chip>
<Chip variant="green">Loop</Chip>
<Chip variant="unique">UNIQUE</Chip>`}</code></pre>
  </section>

  {/* ─────── Accordion ─────── */}
  <section class="showcase-section" id="accordion">
    <h3>Accordion</h3>
    <p>Collapsible section dùng <code>&lt;details&gt;/&lt;summary&gt;</code> — progressive enhancement, works without JS. Dùng cho failure modes, implementation recipe, FAQ.</p>
    <div class="example-render">
      <Accordion title="Failure modes & edge cases">
        <p>Nội dung ẩn mặc định. Mở ra khi click tiêu đề.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Edge case 1: timeout khi model trả về quá chậm</li>
          <li>Edge case 2: template variable typo → literal <code>{`{KEY}`}</code> còn sót</li>
        </ul>
      </Accordion>
      <Accordion title="Implementation recipe" defaultOpen={true}>
        <p>Section này mở sẵn vì <code>defaultOpen=true</code>.</p>
      </Accordion>
    </div>
    <pre class="example-code"><code>{`<Accordion title="Failure modes">
  <p>Nội dung collapse...</p>
</Accordion>

<Accordion title="Recipe" defaultOpen={true}>
  <p>Mở sẵn khi load.</p>
</Accordion>`}</code></pre>
  </section>

  {/* ─────── KeyTakeaway ─────── */}
  <section class="showcase-section" id="keytakeaway">
    <h3>KeyTakeaway</h3>
    <p>Hộp tóm tắt điểm chính cuối section — mỗi item render <code>✓</code> + HTML. Đặt trước <code>RefList</code> hoặc <code>DeepDiveLink</code>.</p>
    <div class="example-render">
      <KeyTakeaway items={[
        'Tool description đóng vai trò như <strong>mini system prompt</strong> cho từng tool',
        'Template variables (<code>{`{PLATFORM}`}</code>, <code>{`{SHELL}`}</code>) inject lúc khởi tạo',
        'Tách file <code>.txt</code> giúp A/B test mà <em>không</em> đổi code',
      ]} />
    </div>
    <pre class="example-code"><code>{`<KeyTakeaway items={[
  'Điểm 1 — HTML hỗ trợ <strong>bold</strong>',
  'Điểm 2 — <code>code</code> inline',
]} />`}</code></pre>
  </section>

  {/* ─────── QuoteBlock ─────── */}
  <section class="showcase-section" id="quoteblock">
    <h3>QuoteBlock</h3>
    <p>Pull quote với attribution và source link. Dùng để trích dẫn paper, blog, keynote — tạo visual anchor trong nội dung dài.</p>
    <div class="example-render">
      <QuoteBlock
        quote="The model doesn't know what it doesn't know — the harness must constrain the solution space so the agent doesn't wander into failure modes."
        author="Avi Chawla"
        source="https://blog.dailydoseofds.com/p/the-anatomy-of-an-agent-harness"
        sourceLabel="The Anatomy of an Agent Harness"
      />
    </div>
    <pre class="example-code"><code>{`<QuoteBlock
  quote="The model doesn't know what it doesn't know..."
  author="Avi Chawla"
  source="https://blog.dailydoseofds.com/..."
  sourceLabel="The Anatomy of an Agent Harness"
/>`}</code></pre>
  </section>

  {/* ─────── StepList ─────── */}
  <section class="showcase-section" id="steplist">
    <h3>StepList</h3>
    <p>Visual numbered steps với connector line và optional code snippet per step. Dùng cho implementation recipe, how-to, migration guide.</p>
    <div class="example-render">
      <StepList steps={[
        { title: 'Tạo file .txt cạnh .ts', description: 'Đặt description ra file riêng, cùng thư mục với implementation.', code: 'touch tool/bash.txt', lang: 'bash' },
        { title: 'Import trong .ts', description: 'Bun hỗ trợ text import native. Node.js cần readFileSync.', code: `import DESCRIPTION from "./bash.txt"` },
        { title: 'Inject template variables', description: 'Render lúc tool khởi tạo, không phải mỗi lần gọi.' },
      ]} />
    </div>
    <pre class="example-code"><code>{`<StepList steps={[
  { title: 'Bước 1', description: 'Mô tả', code: 'npm install', lang: 'bash' },
  { title: 'Bước 2', description: 'Mô tả tiếp' },
]} />`}</code></pre>
  </section>

  {/* ─────── Timeline ─────── */}
  <section class="showcase-section" id="timeline">
    <h3>Timeline</h3>
    <p>Vertical timeline với dot markers + connector. Dùng cho lịch sử phát triển, evolution of techniques, chronological narrative.</p>
    <div class="example-render">
      <Timeline items={[
        { date: '2023-Q1', title: 'LangChain ra mắt', description: 'Framework đầu tiên cho LLM chaining, giới thiệu khái niệm chain và agent abstractions.', tag: 'Milestone' },
        { date: '2024-Q1', title: 'OpenAI Function Calling', description: 'Structured tool calling trở thành tiêu chuẩn — thay thế ReAct prompting thủ công.', tag: 'Standard' },
        { date: '2024-Q3', title: 'Claude Code & opencode', description: 'Harness engineering với vòng lặp agent chặt chẽ, streaming, và multi-turn context.', tag: 'Modern' },
      ]} />
    </div>
    <pre class="example-code"><code>{`<Timeline items={[
  { date: '2024-Q1', title: 'Milestone', description: 'Mô tả...', tag: 'Label' },
]} />`}</code></pre>
  </section>

  </section>
